月年终奖，2年涨了2000块钱，最后提离职还要给我涨呢我润回老家了，你这仨月被开不是过年肯定就没年终奖，迟到我也被说过八点半没到哈哈最后倒也没扣钱","createdAt":"2023-09-19T20:20:03"},{"id":"01963de6-af41-71a8-8e82-631514b28d00","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3716,"content":"这是被PUA魔怔了 还是腿子？","createdAt":"2023-09-20T15:55:38"},{"id":"01963de6-ab8a-7172-b777-5583e790d8b7","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":3158,"content":"4年半9K?","createdAt":"2023-09-20T16:49:14"},{"id":"01963de6-af45-73f8-bb1d-31925e6bdcec","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":4253,"content":"腿子哥吗？PUA 了？","createdAt":"2023-11-03T15:37:33"},{"id":"01963de6-af4e-7125-8e08-6d2b96751106","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":6079,"content":"今天刚面试完！","createdAt":"2023-11-06T23:54:22"},{"id":"01963de6-af96-717a-9b24-9d1fc4e27c09","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":6079,"content":"结果咋样","createdAt":"2023-11-07T17:47:27"},{"id":"01963de6-af9b-73ec-8bca-6d8813d77b3b","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":5884,"content":"是人就要、只要是活的、没病就要","createdAt":"2023-11-14T15:38:37"},{"id":"01963de6-af9f-7227-8130-cbf5ad62351c","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7071,"content":"是联合财富广场的吗","createdAt":"2024-04-01T18:14:49"},{"id":"01963de6-af4a-730c-8e2e-fdb9de92ecd5","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":2783,"content":"当狗习惯了?","createdAt":"2024-04-02T11:17:01"},{"id":"01963de6-afa3-7394-b9be-9e132d35e185","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21423,"content":"这个公司现在咋样，考虑要不要过去面试。。。知道的，踢一脚","createdAt":"2024-07-19T08:25:45"},{"id":"01963de6-afe7-736d-9f06-949c2c269b4f","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":21396,"content":"加班巨狠","createdAt":"2024-07-19T09:51:19"},{"id":"01963de6-afeb-717c-9148-8f19de56ed9a","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":7098,"content":"够能改得了吃屎吗？现在以后未来，直到倒闭都这个德性。","createdAt":"2024-08-30T17:31:30"},{"id":"01981c22-9261-7060-b8ff-5ab0e73be230","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":22913,"content":"怎么感觉是披着自研公司的包装，做着外包的工作","createdAt":"2025-07-18T14:04:44"},{"id":"01981c53-9d7a-718c-b8c2-a0d7bbccfa95","parentId":null,"rootId":null,"fromId":24709,